  "instructions": [
    "Cook the white rice according to package instructions and set it aside.",
    "In a pan, melt the unsalted butter over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced shio-cured pork belly and cook until lightly browned, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped prunes and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Add the gochujang, soy sauce, and brown sugar to the pan and stir to combine.",
    "Add the chopped kimchi and cook for 1-2 minutes, until slightly softened.",
    "To assemble the bibimbap, place a scoop of cooked white rice in the bottom of a bowl.",
    "Add a spoonful of the pork and prune mixture on top of the rice.",
    "Top with sliced avocado, chopped green onions, and shredded cheddar cheese.",
    "Drizzle with additional gochujang if desired.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
